10#include <stdio.h>
11#include "internal/cryptlib.h"
12#include <openssl/evp.h>
13#include <openssl/x509.h>
14#include "internal/asn1_int.h"
15#include "internal/evp_int.h"
16
17int i2d_PrivateKey(EVP_PKEY *a, unsigned char **pp)
18{
19 if (a->ameth && a->ameth->old_priv_encode) {
20 return a->ameth->old_priv_encode(a, pp);
21 }
22 if (a->ameth && a->ameth->priv_encode) {
23 PKCS8_PRIV_KEY_INFO *p8 = EVP_PKEY2PKCS8(a);
24 int ret = 0;
25 if (p8 != NULL) {
26 ret = i2d_PKCS8_PRIV_KEY_INFO(p8, pp);
27 PKCS8_PRIV_KEY_INFO_free(p8);
28 }
29 return ret;
30 }
31 ASN1err(ASN1_F_I2D_PRIVATEKEY, ASN1_R_UNSUPPORTED_PUBLIC_KEY_TYPE);
32 return -1;
33}
